  "body": "**Syncing Is Too Slow**\r\nAfter Bedrock there effectively are no publicly available snapshots that are usable. The official OP Labs snapshot is 4 months out of date and the abysmal state of Optimism's syncing means any user would need to wait months for a sync to complete which is a non starter. Are there any available snapshots that are more recent or alternative ways to sync faster? Other chains offer snap sync, frankly it's hard to comprehend how this hasn't been prioritized to make this chain usable.\r\n\r\n",
